---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Business Intelligence Systems - intelio">
<main>
  <!-- HERO SECTION (Dark) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-normal mb-4 sm:mb-6">Business Intelligence Systems</h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-400">Visibility that drives decisions—not just reports that document the past.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: What Breaks (Light) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-white text-black">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-6 sm:mb-8">What Breaks</h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">Most organizations operate with:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Data spread across CRMs, accounting systems, project tools, spreadsheets, and inboxes</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Reporting that is late, manual, or incomplete</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Leadership decisions based on partial information or intuition</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">As complexity increases, visibility decreases. The business grows, but clarity collapses.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: What We Build (Dark) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-6 sm:mb-8">What We Build</h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">We design business intelligence systems that consolidate operational, financial, and performance data into a single decision layer.</p>
      <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">This includes:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Unified dashboards across departments</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>KPIs tied directly to real workflows (not vanity metrics)</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Automated reporting pipelines</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Drill-down visibility from executive level to transaction level</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Alerts and signals when performance deviates from expectations</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: How It Works (Light) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-white text-black">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-6 sm:mb-8">How It Works</h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">We start by mapping how information is created, moved, and used inside the business. Then we design systems that surface the right information at the right time—without manual effort.</p>
      <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">AI is used selectively for:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Pattern detection</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Anomaly identification</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Forecasting and scenario analysis</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: The Impact (Dark) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-6 sm:mb-8">The Impact</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span class="text-lg">Leaders see the business clearly</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span class="text-lg">Decisions happen faster</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span class="text-lg">Problems are caught early</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span class="text-lg">Meetings shift from updates to action</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA SECTION (Light) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-white text-black">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-8 sm:mb-12">Ready to see your business clearly?</h2>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-black text-white text-base sm:text-lg font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors min-h-[56px]">
        Work with Intelio
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
</Layout>

